info: Rating, 4 stars,  · 3 weeks ago,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment: Enjoyable stay. The host was quickly responsive and flexible. Staff were, too. Cozy hotel worth its price.
Dirt everywhere. Dirty basin, bath room, one towel for 5 person. No cleaning at all.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2024,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: The room was big and the check-in super easy. Everyone was very friendly to me and the host always responded very quickly. I recommend the place, even if you have to get used to the fact that the other guests are always very loud and the wifi does not always work. Still great place to stay .
